<i>noun</i>: 수줍음 [수주븜], 부끄럼 [부끄럼], 부끄러움 [부끄러움] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>수줍음 [수주븜]</dt><br>
<dd>shyness; bashfulness</dd><br>
<dd>다른 사람 앞에서 말이나 행동을 하는 것을 어려워하거나 부끄러워하는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being uncomfortable with talking or acting in front of other people or being shy about it.</dd><br>
<dt>부끄럼 [부끄럼]</dt><br>
<dd>shyness; bashfulness</dd><br>
<dd>부끄러워하는 느낌이나 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>The feeling of being shy or the state of mind of being shy.</dd><br>
<dt>부끄러움 [부끄러움]</dt><br>
<dd>shyness; bashfulness</dd><br>
<dd>부끄러워하는 느낌이나 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>The feeling or state of mind of being shy.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>